      "acceptanceCriteria": "Constitutive model selection justified by literature; plasticity representation validated against coupon data for Ti-6Al-4V.",
      "rationale": "Bilinear isotropic hardening plasticity (Ti-6Al-4V: E=114 GPa, σ_y=880 MPa, E_t=2.1 GPa) selected based on published material characterization. Coupon-level FEA vs. tensile test comparison shows <4% error in yield and ultimate force. Model form uncertainty quantified via sensitivity to tangent modulus ±15%. Gradation 3 achieved."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Model inputs",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
