      "rationale": "Testing performed under a single ASTM F1717 loading configuration (10° off-axis compression-bending). Only one test condition was applied due to resource constraints; a second loading angle was not evaluated. Achieved Gradation 2 against required Gradation 3 — identified gap documented and accepted by sponsor with rationale that the single condition is the regulatory standard condition."
