      "rationale": "Test fixture compliance measured via instrumented dummy specimen and incorporated into FEA as a spring boundary condition (k_fixture = 4,820 N/mm). Angular alignment verified to within 0.2° of nominal 10°. Equivalency confirmed quantitatively. Gradation 3 achieved."
