    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed required levels. The single deficiency (Test conditions, achieved Gradation 2 vs. required Gradation 3) is accepted with documented justification that ASTM F1717 specifies a single loading configuration and that the test condition is the regulatory standard. All three primary QoIs satisfy E/uval < 1.96 and <10% difference criteria. The credibility evidence is sufficient to support the regulatory submission claim. Post-signature supplemental evidence (Lab 2 re-analysis, evidenceTimestamp 2026-05-02) was incorporated without re-signing; the assessment team noted this update but did not invalidate the original decision.",
